Xabi Alonso believes Bayern Munich team-mate Manuel Neuer deserves to win the 2014 Ballon d'Or after playing a major role in Germany's World Cup triumph.

Cristiano Ronaldo and Lionel Messi are favourites to win the Ballon d'Or, however Alonso has made a case for the German stopper to break the duo's six-year dominance of winning the award.  

'If Manuel won it, it'd be totally deserved,' Alonso told Sport Bild.

